702
00:31:05,240 --> 00:31:05,800
Luís Montenegro,

703
00:31:06,040 --> 00:31:06,060
acaba...

704
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:11,980
este debate e quer saber se o Gabinete de Estudos

705
00:31:11,980 --> 00:31:14,180
